{"tid":843744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鎖國行動展開！小米封死跨地域刷機  大批新舊手機受影響","createTime":"2018-10-01T11:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T17:05:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"10a79c927e78eedf3f48030a5a33ca4df7e6cc84","tid":843744,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/211530/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4568%2F211530%2F1&d=wxCBMOCrh%2F4zoxv4IeR4H57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=829e33f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/211530/1</a>/<br />\n<br />\n鎖國行動展開！小米封死跨地域刷機  大批新舊手機受影響<br />\n<br />\n虎仔(uniqlo) 2018-10-01 11:54<br />\n<br />\n雖然小米在香港掛牌上市，又有專門店和行貨在香港銷售，不過售賣的產品款式始終不及大陸多。有消費者於是嘗試透過水貨商購入大陸版手機，甚至直接在大陸購買，然後再嘗試以刷機方式換上國際版的 ROM，不過這方式已經行不通，小米的「鎖國行動」經已開始。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.tw/hk/mobile/img/2018-10/01/211530/uniqlo_1_741f4bf3071c009b5f251b4a99aef1fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.tw%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2018-10%2F01%2F211530%2Funiqlo_1_741f4bf3071c009b5f251b4a99aef1fe.jpg&h=59171e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸傳媒報導指，小米日前為旗下多款手機加入 Anti-Rollback Protection 防回溯保護機制，禁止用戶將手機 MIUI 系統降級，以往降級刷機的方案被封殺，很大機會因此變磚。大陸傳媒亦提到小米在 9 月中曾經在論壇張貼公告，表示跨區域刷機亦被禁止。以往不少大陸用戶因為種種原因，都會將手上的國行版手機刷國際版 ROM，現在無論是大陸機刷國際 ROM，還是國際版手機刷大陸 ROM 都不再允許。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.tw/hk/mobile/img/2018-10/01/211530/uniqlo_1_e40caf140b88ba319552489ec89cac64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.tw%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2018-10%2F01%2F211530%2Funiqlo_1_e40caf140b88ba319552489ec89cac64.png&h=38dc8bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n著名刷機網站 XDA Developers 進行了實測，國行手機刷國際 ROM 會卡死在 Recovery 界面，並且顯示「This MIUI version can&rsquo;t be installed on this device」。XiaoMiTool 開發者 franztesca 發現小米新增了一段區域對照碼，他表示要繞過限制要先為 Bootloader 解鎖，然後用 TWRP、fastbook 或 MiFlash 等工具刷機。如果在刷機期間變磚，則只有 EDL 緊急下載模式方能自救，不過 EDL 我食只對極少數小米帳號開放權限。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.tw/hk/mobile/img/2018-10/01/211530/uniqlo_1_5f6060cfd1cbe32e3114664a7df87ed1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.tw%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2018-10%2F01%2F211530%2Funiqlo_1_5f6060cfd1cbe32e3114664a7df87ed1.png&h=dae59079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時已知道受影響無法刷機的手機型號包括：小米 6X (&ldquo;wayne&rdquo;)、小米 8 (&ldquo;dipper&rdquo;)、小米 8 EE、小米 8 透明探索版 (&ldquo;ursa&rdquo;)、小米 8 SE (&ldquo;sirius&rdquo;)、小米 8 Lite、小米 8 青春版 (&ldquo;platina&rdquo;)、小米 8 Pro、小米 8 屏幕指纹板 (&ldquo;equuleus&rdquo;)、小米 Max 3 (&ldquo;nitrogen&rdquo;)、小米 Mix 2S (&ldquo;polaris&rdquo;)、小米平板 4 / Mi Pad 4 Plus (&ldquo;clover&rdquo;)、Poco F1 / Pocophone F1 (&ldquo;beryllium&rdquo;)、紅米 Note 5A (&ldquo;ugg&rdquo;)、紅米 Y1 Lite (&ldquo;ugglite&rdquo;)、紅米 Y2 / 紅米 S2 (&ldquo;ysl&rdquo;)、紅米 5 (&ldquo;rosy&rdquo;)、紅米 5A (&ldquo;riva&rdquo;)、紅米 6 (&ldquo;cereus&rdquo;)、紅米 6A (&ldquo;cactus&rdquo;)、紅米 6 Pro (&ldquo;sakura&rdquo; and &ldquo;sakura_india&rdquo;)、紅米 Note 5 / Redmi 5 Plus (&ldquo;vince&rdquo;)、紅米 Note 5 Pro / Redmi Note 5 AI (&ldquo;whyred&rdquo;)、紅米 Note 6 Pro (&ldquo;tulip&rdquo;)。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：cnbeta"},{"pid":"88c991bb5cf59544e2c51f3f684d300c474f40c1","tid":843744,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761ccc0365ff1a75ec46a2e235f78d1e4e77d721","tid":843744,"uid":1834,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"小米好啊，又平又靚，性價比高iphone幾多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781de6d9d9ca9d25964ebcac344fd7efa5ab09d0","tid":843744,"uid":55924,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"行得直企得直驚佢偷咩"},{"pid":"3bf0c73c6803643858b11fa4a3c9933f372c249c","tid":843744,"uid":59511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:07:22.000Z","msg":"解左bootloader就刷得，對以前刷開機只係麻煩左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過用得小米通常都智力有啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6d8a55093ed56fd292892ba68b3427c8397e55","tid":843744,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2018/05/180504_mikh_06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2018%2F05%2F180504_mikh_06.jpg&h=587fb55b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c90e74ab8eca40d72b103735e06698d8e960d5","tid":843744,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15840a48f4f396ee346c0e4aedd96b9af9454d01","tid":843744,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30469ba11d9d67ebdfb8bea966012becadac8aad","tid":843744,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a6d8a55093ed56fd292892ba68b3427c8397e55",